Dialogue: 1,0:14:45.70,0:14:49.96,signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1126,171)\fscx117\fscy117\fnPen of Truth\c&HF8B085&\3c&HB06B44&\blur0.75}Wants to go in, \Nbut can't
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.70,0:14:49.96,signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(174,80)\fscx89\fscy89\fnPen of Truth\b1\bord1\c&H9396C9&\3c&H9396C9&\blur0.65}*Unsure if it's okay to\N enter a house where\N a girl's sleeping
